title: Lifetime-Jodi Arias Dirty Little Secret [2013]
description:
Lifetime-Jodi Arias Dirty Little Secret

Air Date: 22 June 2013

Summary:  Jodi Arias: Dirty Little Secret is a ripped-from-cable-news saga of a woman scorned who last month was found guilty of killing her former lover, motivational speaker Travis Alexander. On June 4, 2008, Arias stabbed and slashed him nearly 30 times, slit his throat and shot him in the head in what prosecutors said was jealous rage, and what Arias unpersuasively argued was self-defense, when, according to her, he attacked her. 

But you know all that. 

Dirty Little Secret unearths no secrets, dirty or otherwise. Every sordid detail, it seems, has been trumpeted for years by the media, then recycled for months during Arias' trial in Phoenix that got blanket coverage on TV and in particular on cable's HLN, vaulting that network to record ratings. 



Cast: 

Tania Raymonde ... Jodi Arias

Jesse Lee Soffer ... Travis Alexander 

Tony Plana ..Prosecutor Juan Martinez 

David Zayas ... Detective Esteban Flores
